         - Replace POST-LINK-1 with the page/post URL\n             - Replace \"Description 1\" with a short description\n             ========================================== -->\n            <a href=\"POST-LINK-1\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/hero_dummy1.png\" alt=\"Description 1\">\n            </a>\n        <!-- ==========================================\n             SLIDE 2\n             - Replace IMAGE-URL-2 with your Canva poster URL\n             - Replace POST-LINK-2 with the page/post URL\n             - Replace \"Description 2\" with a short description\n             ========================================== -->\n            <a href=\"POST-LINK-2\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/hero_dummy2.png\" alt=\"Description 2\">\n            </a>\n        <!-- PASTE ADDITIONAL SLIDES HERE (max 3 more) -->\n    <button onclick=\"satuPrev()\">&#8249;</button>\n    <button onclick=\"satuNext()\">&#8250;</button>\n        <!-- ADD ONE MORE DOT HERE FOR EACH NEW SLIDE YOU ADD -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 3:  -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 4:  -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 5:  -->','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','23-revision-v1','','','2026-05-20 07:25:48','2026-05-20 07:25:48','',23,'http://10.18.33.196/?p=45',0,'revision','',0),
(46,1,'2026-05-20 07:25:49','2026-05-20 07:25:49','<!--\n=============================================================\nSATU WEBSITE - HOMEPAGE SLIDER\n=============================================================\nMANAGED BY: Dean IR Office, IIT Bombay\nLAST UPDATED: May 2026\nHOW THIS SLIDER WORKS:\n- Each slide is a  block\n- Each slide contains one image (your Canva poster)\n- Clicking the image takes the visitor to the related post/page\n- The slider auto-plays every 5 seconds\n- There are previous/next arrows and dot indicators\nCANVA POSTER DIMENSIONS:\n- Use 1400 x 500 pixels in Canva (Landscape format)\n- Export as PNG or JPG\n- Upload via WP Admin → Media → Add New\n- Copy the file URL from the media library\n=============================================================\nHOW TO ADD A NEW SLIDE (currently 2 slides, max 5):\n=============================================================\n1. Design your poster in Canva (1400 x 500 px)\n2. Upload it via WP Admin → Media → Add New\n3. Copy the image URL from the media library\n4. Copy the block below and paste it before the closing\n    of id=\"satuSliderTrack\":\n       <a href=\"PASTE-YOUR-POST-LINK-HERE\" target=\"_blank\">\n           <img src=\"PASTE-YOUR-IMAGE-URL-HERE\" alt=\"Brief description\">\n       </a>\n5. Also add a new dot indicator inside id=\"satuDots\":\n   Replace N with the slide number starting from 0\n   (slide 1 = 0, slide 2 = 1, slide 3 = 2, and so on)\n=============================================================\nHOW TO REMOVE A SLIDE:\n=============================================================\nDelete the entire ... block\nand remove the last  from id=\"satuDots\"\n=============================================================\nHOW TO CHANGE THE AUTO-PLAY SPEED:\n=============================================================\nAt the bottom of this file, find:\n   satuInterval = setInterval(satuNext, 5000);\nChange 5000 to any number (in milliseconds)\nExample: 3000 = 3 seconds, 7000 = 7 seconds\n=============================================================\n-->\n<style>\n.satu-slider-wrapper {\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n    background: #111;\n    user-select: none;\n}\n.satu-slider-track {\n    display: flex;\n    transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out;\n    will-change: transform;\n}\n.satu-slide {\n    min-width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n}\n.satu-slide a {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n}\n.satu-slide img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    object-fit: cover;\n}\n/* ─── Arrows ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-arrow {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 50%;\n    transform: translateY(-50%);\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);\n    color: #fff;\n    border: none;\n    font-size: 1.6rem;\n    padding: 10px 16px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    z-index: 10;\n    border-radius: 3px;\n    transition: background 0.2s ease;\n    line-height: 1;\n}\n.satu-arrow:hover { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); }\n.satu-arrow.prev { left: 12px; }\n.satu-arrow.next { right: 12px; }\n/* ─── Dots ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-dots {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 10px;\n    width: 100%;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n}\n.satu-dot {\n    width: 10px;\n    height: 10px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;\n    display: inline-block;\n}\n.satu-dot.active {\n    background: #ffffff;\n    transform: scale(1.25);\n}\n/* ─── Mobile ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .satu-arrow { font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 7px 11px; }\n}\n</style>\n<!-- SLIDER HTML — Edit image URLs and links below -->\n        <!-- ==========================================\n             SLIDE 1\n             - Replace IMAGE-URL-1 with your Canva poster URL\n             - Replace POST-LINK-1 with the page/post URL\n             - Replace \"Description 1\" with a short description\n             ========================================== -->\n            <a href=\"POST-LINK-1\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/hero_dummy1.png\" alt=\"Description 1\">\n            </a>\n        <!-- ==========================================\n             SLIDE 2\n             - Replace IMAGE-URL-2 with your Canva poster URL\n             - Replace POST-LINK-2 with the page/post URL\n             - Replace \"Description 2\" with a short description\n             ========================================== -->\n            <a href=\"POST-LINK-2\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/hero_dummy2.png\" alt=\"Description 2\">\n            </a>\n        <!-- PASTE ADDITIONAL SLIDES HERE (max 3 more) -->\n    <button onclick=\"satuPrev()\">&#8249;</button>\n    <button onclick=\"satuNext()\">&#8250;</button>\n        <!-- ADD ONE MORE DOT HERE FOR EACH NEW SLIDE YOU ADD -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 3:  -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 4:  -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 5:  -->\n					<style>\n/* ─── Section Wrapper ────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-cards-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    padding: 60px 48px;\n    background-color: #ffffff;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: stretch;\n    gap: 32px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n/* ─── Individual Card ────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card {\n    flex: 1;\n    max-width: 360px;\n    background-color: #ffffff;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n    padding: 40px 32px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    text-align: center;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    color: inherit;\n    /* Float animation setup */\n    transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease;\n    transform: translateY(0);\n}\n.satu-card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-10px);\n    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(107, 30, 30, 0.18);\n    border-color: #6B1E1E;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    color: inherit;\n}\n/* ─── Card Icon ──────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-icon {\n    width: 64px;\n    height: 64px;\n    background-color: #6B1E1E;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    transition: background-color 0.35s ease;\n}\n.satu-card:hover .satu-card-icon {\n    background-color: #8B2525;\n}\n.satu-card-icon svg {\n    width: 30px;\n    height: 30px;\n    fill: #ffffff;\n}\n/* ─── Card Title ─────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-title {\n    font-family: \"Palatino Linotype\", Palatino, Georgia, serif;\n    font-size: 1.3rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #6B1E1E;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n}\n/* ─── Card Description ───────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-desc {\n    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 0.88rem;\n    color: #555555;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    flex: 1;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n/* ─── Card Button ────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-btn {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 9px 24px;\n    background-color: #6B1E1E;\n    color: #ffffff !important;\n    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 0.82rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    text-decoration: none !important;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    transition: background-color 0.25s ease;\n    margin-top: auto;\n}\n.satu-card:hover .satu-card-btn {\n    background-color: #8B2525;\n}\n/* ─── Tablet ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n@media (max-width: 900px) {\n    .satu-cards-section {\n        padding: 48px 28px;\n        gap: 24px;\n    }\n}\n/* ─── Mobile ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n@media (max-width: 650px) {\n    .satu-cards-section {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n        padding: 36px 20px;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .satu-card {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        width: 100%;\n        padding: 32px 24px;\n    }\n}\n</style>\n<section>\n    <!-- ── Card 1: About SATU ── -->\n    <a href=\"/about-satu/\">\n            <!-- Info / About icon -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10\n                         10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z\"/>\n            </svg>\n        About SATU\n            Learn about the SATU Presidents\' Forum — its vision, mission,\n            member universities across Southeast and South Asia and Taiwan,\n            and IIT Bombay\'s role in this academic alliance.\n        Learn More\n    </a>\n    <!-- ── Card 2: Activities ── -->\n    <a href=\"/activities/\">\n            <!-- Calendar / Activities icon -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M19 3h-1V1h-2v2H8V1H6v2H5C3.89 3 3 3.9 3 5v14\n                         c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0\n                         16H5V8h14v11zM7 10h5v5H7z\"/>\n            </svg>\n        Activities\n            Explore SATU\'s academic exchanges, joint research initiatives,\n            webinar series, innovation competitions, and upcoming events\n            hosted by member universities.\n        Explore\n    </a>\n    <!-- ── Card 3: Previous Website ── -->\n    <a href=\"https://satu.ncku.edu.tw/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <!-- External link icon -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M19 19H5V5h7V3H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0\n                         002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7h-2v7zM14 3v2h3.59\n                         l-9.83 9.83 1.41 1.41L19 6.41V10h2V3h-7z\"/>\n            </svg>\n        Previous Website\n            Visit the original SATU Presidents\' Forum website hosted by\n            National Cheng Kung University (NCKU), Taiwan for archives,\n            past events, and historical records.\n        Visit\n    </a>\n</section>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','23-revision-v1','','','2026-05-20 07:25:49','2026-05-20 07:25:49','',23,'http://10.18.33.196/?p=46',0,'revision','',0),
(48,1,'2026-05-20 07:31:37','2026-05-20 07:31:37','<!--\n=============================================================\nSATU WEBSITE - HOMEPAGE SLIDER\n=============================================================\nMANAGED BY: Dean IR Office, IIT Bombay\nLAST UPDATED: May 2026\nHOW THIS SLIDER WORKS:\n- Each slide is a  block\n- Each slide contains one image (your Canva poster)\n- Clicking the image takes the visitor to the related post/page\n- The slider auto-plays every 5 seconds\n- There are previous/next arrows and dot indicators\nCANVA POSTER DIMENSIONS:\n- Use 1400 x 500 pixels in Canva (Landscape format)\n- Export as PNG or JPG\n- Upload via WP Admin → Media → Add New\n- Copy the file URL from the media library\n=============================================================\nHOW TO ADD A NEW SLIDE (currently 2 slides, max 5):\n=============================================================\n1. Design your poster in Canva (1400 x 500 px)\n2. Upload it via WP Admin → Media → Add New\n3. Copy the image URL from the media library\n4. Copy the block below and paste it before the closing\n    of id=\"satuSliderTrack\":\n       <a href=\"PASTE-YOUR-POST-LINK-HERE\" target=\"_blank\">\n           <img src=\"PASTE-YOUR-IMAGE-URL-HERE\" alt=\"Brief description\">\n       </a>\n5. Also add a new dot indicator inside id=\"satuDots\":\n   Replace N with the slide number starting from 0\n   (slide 1 = 0, slide 2 = 1, slide 3 = 2, and so on)\n=============================================================\nHOW TO REMOVE A SLIDE:\n=============================================================\nDelete the entire ... block\nand remove the last  from id=\"satuDots\"\n=============================================================\nHOW TO CHANGE THE AUTO-PLAY SPEED:\n=============================================================\nAt the bottom of this file, find:\n   satuInterval = setInterval(satuNext, 5000);\nChange 5000 to any number (in milliseconds)\nExample: 3000 = 3 seconds, 7000 = 7 seconds\n=============================================================\n-->\n<style>\n.satu-slider-wrapper {\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n    background: #111;\n    user-select: none;\n}\n.satu-slider-track {\n    display: flex;\n    transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out;\n    will-change: transform;\n}\n.satu-slide {\n    min-width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n}\n.satu-slide a {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n}\n.satu-slide img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    object-fit: cover;\n}\n/* ─── Arrows ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-arrow {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 50%;\n    transform: translateY(-50%);\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);\n    color: #fff;\n    border: none;\n    font-size: 1.6rem;\n    padding: 10px 16px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    z-index: 10;\n    border-radius: 3px;\n    transition: background 0.2s ease;\n    line-height: 1;\n}\n.satu-arrow:hover { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); }\n.satu-arrow.prev { left: 12px; }\n.satu-arrow.next { right: 12px; }\n/* ─── Dots ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-dots {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 10px;\n    width: 100%;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n}\n.satu-dot {\n    width: 10px;\n    height: 10px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;\n    display: inline-block;\n}\n.satu-dot.active {\n    background: #ffffff;\n    transform: scale(1.25);\n}\n/* ─── Mobile ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .satu-arrow { font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 7px 11px; }\n}\n</style>\n<!-- SLIDER HTML — Edit image URLs and links below -->\n        <!-- ==========================================\n             SLIDE 1\n             - Replace IMAGE-URL-1 with your Canva poster URL\n             - Replace POST-LINK-1 with the page/post URL\n             - Replace \"Description 1\" with a short description\n             ========================================== -->\n            <a href=\"POST-LINK-1\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/hero_dummy1.png\" alt=\"Description 1\">\n            </a>\n        <!-- ==========================================\n             SLIDE 2\n             - Replace IMAGE-URL-2 with your Canva poster URL\n             - Replace POST-LINK-2 with the page/post URL\n             - Replace \"Description 2\" with a short description\n             ========================================== -->\n            <a href=\"POST-LINK-2\" target=\"_blank\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/hero_dummy2.png\" alt=\"Description 2\">\n            </a>\n        <!-- PASTE ADDITIONAL SLIDES HERE (max 3 more) -->\n    <button onclick=\"satuPrev()\">&#8249;</button>\n    <button onclick=\"satuNext()\">&#8250;</button>\n        <!-- ADD ONE MORE DOT HERE FOR EACH NEW SLIDE YOU ADD -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 3:  -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 4:  -->\n        <!-- Example for slide 5:  -->\n					<style>\n/* ─── Section Wrapper ────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-cards-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    padding: 60px 48px;\n    background-color: #ffffff;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: stretch;\n    gap: 32px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n/* ─── Individual Card ────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card {\n    flex: 1;\n    max-width: 360px;\n    background-color: #ffffff;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n    padding: 40px 32px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    text-align: center;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    color: inherit;\n    /* Float animation setup */\n    transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease;\n    transform: translateY(0);\n}\n.satu-card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-10px);\n    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(107, 30, 30, 0.18);\n    border-color: #6B1E1E;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    color: inherit;\n}\n/* ─── Card Icon ──────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-icon {\n    width: 64px;\n    height: 64px;\n    background-color: #6B1E1E;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    transition: background-color 0.35s ease;\n}\n.satu-card:hover .satu-card-icon {\n    background-color: #8B2525;\n}\n.satu-card-icon svg {\n    width: 30px;\n    height: 30px;\n    fill: #ffffff;\n}\n/* ─── Card Title ─────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-title {\n    font-family: \"Palatino Linotype\", Palatino, Georgia, serif;\n    font-size: 1.3rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #6B1E1E;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n}\n/* ─── Card Description ───────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-desc {\n    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 0.88rem;\n    color: #555555;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    flex: 1;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n/* ─── Card Button ────────────────────────────────────────── */\n.satu-card-btn {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 9px 24px;\n    background-color: #6B1E1E;\n    color: #ffffff !important;\n    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 0.82rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    text-decoration: none !important;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    transition: background-color 0.25s ease;\n    margin-top: auto;\n}\n.satu-card:hover .satu-card-btn {\n    background-color: #8B2525;\n}\n/* ─── Tablet ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n@media (max-width: 900px) {\n    .satu-cards-section {\n        padding: 48px 28px;\n        gap: 24px;\n    }\n}\n/* ─── Mobile ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */\n@media (max-width: 650px) {\n    .satu-cards-section {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n        padding: 36px 20px;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .satu-card {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        width: 100%;\n        padding: 32px 24px;\n    }\n}\n</style>\n<section>\n    <!-- ── Card 1: About SATU ── -->\n    <a href=\"/about-satu/\">\n            <!-- Info / About icon -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10\n                         10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z\"/>\n            </svg>\n        About SATU\n            Learn about the SATU Presidents\' Forum — its vision, mission,\n            member universities across Southeast and South Asia and Taiwan,\n            and IIT Bombay\'s role in this academic alliance.\n        Learn More\n    </a>\n    <!-- ── Card 2: Activities ── -->\n    <a href=\"/activities/\">\n            <!-- Calendar / Activities icon -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M19 3h-1V1h-2v2H8V1H6v2H5C3.89 3 3 3.9 3 5v14\n                         c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0\n                         16H5V8h14v11zM7 10h5v5H7z\"/>\n            </svg>\n        Activities\n            Explore SATU\'s academic exchanges, joint research initiatives,\n            webinar series, innovation competitions, and upcoming events\n            hosted by member universities.\n        Explore\n    </a>\n    <!-- ── Card 3: Previous Website ── -->\n    <a href=\"https://satu.ncku.edu.tw/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <!-- External link icon -->\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M19 19H5V5h7V3H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0\n                         002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7h-2v7zM14 3v2h3.59\n                         l-9.83 9.83 1.41 1.41L19 6.41V10h2V3h-7z\"/>\n            </svg>\n        Previous Website\n            Visit the original SATU Presidents\' Forum website hosted by\n            National Cheng Kung University (NCKU), Taiwan for archives,\n            past events, and historical records.\n        Visit\n    </a>\n</section>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','23-revision-v1','','','2026-05-20 07:31:37','2026-05-20 07:31:37','',23,'http://10.18.33.196/?p=48',0,'revision','',0),
